# Example crontab — install with `crontab -e` and paste these lines.
#
# Daily SKT report at 7:00 AM (server time). Adjust hour/minute as needed.
# Wrap absolute path because cron does NOT inherit your shell's cwd.

# Make sure Homebrew bins and node tools are findable.
PATH=/opt/homebrew/bin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin

# Daily 07:00 SKT report. Output appended to scheduler/last-run.log.
0 7 * * * /Users/cody/presentations/20260514/demo/07-agent/scheduler/daily.sh

# Optional: 18:00 market close summary.
# 0 18 * * 1-5 /Users/cody/presentations/20260514/demo/07-agent/scheduler/daily.sh "오늘 KOSPI 종가 기준 통신 3사 시장 동향을 한 페이지로 정리해줘"

# ---
# Manual test (without cron):
#   chmod +x scheduler/daily.sh
#   ./scheduler/daily.sh
#   tail -f scheduler/last-run.log
#
# Cron permissions on macOS:
#   - System Settings → Privacy & Security → Full Disk Access → add /usr/sbin/cron
#     (otherwise cron jobs can't read ~/.claude/ or your project files).
#   - If still failing, prefer launchd (see scheduler/com.aizcorp.agent-demo.daily.plist).
